---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Sectors | Surrey Contracting Limited"
  description="Sectors we work in, commercial, residential, public sector, education, healthcare and retail projects across Surrey."
  path="/sectors"
  active="sectors"
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="page-hero-img" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/surfacing.jpg')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero-vignette"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container page-hero-inner">
    <nav class="crumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M9 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
      <span>Sectors</span>
    </nav>
    <h1 class="page-title">Sectors</h1>
    <p class="page-lede">A contractor that adapts to your sector, programmes, phasing and paperwork built around how your sites actually operate.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Who we work with</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Six sectors, one standard.</h2>
      <p class="section-lede">We've delivered groundworks, earthworks and surfacing across every sector below, each with its own logistics, paperwork and phasing demands. Pick the one that fits.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sector-grid">

      <article class="sector-card">
        <div class="sector-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/hard-landscaping.jpg')"></div>
        <div class="sector-body">
          <h3>Schools</h3>
          <p>Term-bound delivery for nurseries, primaries, secondary and sixth-form sites. Programmes scoped to fit summer holidays and half-terms.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="sector-link">Discuss a schools project →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="sector-card">
        <div class="sector-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/hard-landscaping-2.jpg')"></div>
        <div class="sector-body">
          <h3>Hotel & Leisure</h3>
          <p>Driveway approaches, car parks and external public-realm works delivered around live trading. Out-of-hours options on request.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="sector-link">Discuss a hotel & leisure project →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="sector-card">
        <div class="sector-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/paving.jpg')"></div>
        <div class="sector-body">
          <h3>Retail</h3>
          <p>Car-park refurbishments, service yards and shopfront access works, phased so footfall keeps moving and tenants stay trading.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="sector-link">Discuss a retail project →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="sector-card">
        <div class="sector-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/brickwork.jpeg')"></div>
        <div class="sector-body">
          <h3>Residential</h3>
          <p>From single-plot driveways and gardens to estate roads and adoptable infrastructure for developer-led housing schemes.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="sector-link">Discuss a residential project →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="sector-card">
        <div class="sector-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/surfacing.jpg')"></div>
        <div class="sector-body">
          <h3>Government</h3>
          <p>Local-authority frameworks, schools estates and public-realm works delivered to specification with full audit-grade paperwork.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="sector-link">Discuss a government project →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="sector-card">
        <div class="sector-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/bulk-earthworks.jpg')"></div>
        <div class="sector-body">
          <h3>Commercial</h3>
          <p>Office parks, industrial estates, warehousing and logistics sites, heavy-duty paving, drainage and access infrastructure.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="sector-link">Discuss a commercial project →</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="container cta-strip-row">
    <div>
      <h3>Have a site we should look at?</h3>
      <p>Free measured survey within 5 working days. Itemised proposal soon after.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-strip-ctas">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-yellow">Request a quote</a>
      <a href="tel:01932932650" class="btn btn-ghost-light">01932 932650</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
